Post: #UPDATE as of March 17: With the implementation of the enhanced community quarantine by the Philippine Government, AIA Philam Life has temporarily suspended the operations of our hotline and customer service centers in Luzon until April 12, 2020. Here are branches outside of the quarantine that remain open from Monday to Friday, 10am to 3pm: Cebu, Iloilo*, Ozamis, Cagayan de Oro, General Santos, and Davao*. We remain committed to assisting you on your policy-related needs during these trying times. CLICK on the images below to learn more how we can help you in the coming weeks. IMPORTANT NOTE: *As of March 20, our Ilo-ilo and Davao branches have also temporarily suspended operations.
